# LC Agent

This module contains the core components of the LC Agent, which include the `RunnableNode` and `RunnableNetwork` classes. These classes form the backbone of the LC Agent's processing and network management capabilities.

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

Ensure you have the following prerequisites installed:
- Python 3.10 or higher

### Installation

Clone the repository and install the dependencies:

```bash
git clone https://gitlab-master.nvidia.com/omniverse/gen-ai/lc-agent
cd lc-agent/lc_agent
python setup.py bdist_wheel
```

If you are a developer of this module, you can install it in editable mode:

```bash
git clone https://gitlab-master.nvidia.com/omniverse/gen-ai/lc-agent
cd lc-agent/lc_agent
pip install -e .
```

### Usage

To use the LC Ai Agent, instantiate a `RunnableNetwork` and populate it with `RunnableNode` instances based on your requirements. Refer to the documentation for detailed instructions on creating and managing networks and nodes.

